text: Jacqui Marshall (born 13 March 1957) is an Australian rower. She competed in the women's single sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Australia Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
